Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:03.35,Signs,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Used Bookstore Hitotose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:07.11,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And hup... and hup...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:09.16,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:14.04,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, thanks for helping me \Neven though it's summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:17.12,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm doing this {\i1}because{\i0} it's summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:21.12,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually able to speak in front \Nof people at the culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:23.71,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I bet I could \Nwait on customers, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.18,0:00:26.78,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:31.17,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd like you to help me \Nset out and restock merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:33.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:07.98,sign_2949_11_Trying_Too_Hard,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Trying Too Hard
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:12.36,Signs,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Used Bookstore Hitotose
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:12.36,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, do you want to \Npractice waiting on customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:14.22,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:18.12,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, try doing what you'd do \Nif a customer came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:18.86,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:22.85,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,W-Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:27.10,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,We have old books, \Nrare books... lots of books!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:30.25,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Please take your time looking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:33.04,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That was very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:35.75,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I did it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:36.76,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.30,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:42.48,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:44.89,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a book I'm looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:48.08,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome. We'll be right with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:49.29,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-cha—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:55.77,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, w-we'll be right with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:59.95,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do something with these...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:02.66,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:05.44,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:07.41,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:10.63,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:14.74,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I was so nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:17.54,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help the customer at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:19.91,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that was only the first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:21.68,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get used to it eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.05,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:27.92,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, that's just Mayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:29.56,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:31.44,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.44,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.54,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, where's Aki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:37.21,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The landlady?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.82,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She came back, then headed right out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.54,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What? Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:42.85,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:45.70,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed like she was going to \Nhang out with some theater buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:48.24,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Did you need her for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:51.00,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing in particular...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:55.33,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that the two of us\N haven't hung out lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:58.11,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You're lonely because she \Nhasn't paid attention to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:02.42,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? O-Of course not! I'm not a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.22,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.47,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not bluffing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.70,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:10.85,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:14.48,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! You're ganging up on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:22.24,sign_6102_60_Used_Bookstore_H,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Used Bookstore Hitotose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:18.06,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, are you guys hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:20.48,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we take a break and have some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:22.24,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We'd love some!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You're back to your usual look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:32.12,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing you dressed \Nlike a maid just feels right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:35.40,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You like frilly clothes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:37.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to see you in a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:40.00,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you'd look good in lolita fashion, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:43.63,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,A dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.06,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Lolita...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:49.26,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do that! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:52.64,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,How would it be any different \Nfrom what she's wearing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:55.15,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hinako! Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:57.43,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-sama is here to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:58.65,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better thank...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.05,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.01,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako, what's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:04.78,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, that's Yua-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:07.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just you, Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:10.28,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to pick a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.58,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,So you really do run a café, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.79,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, Yua-chan, help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:23.22,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,So everyone living in the apartments\Nhere also works in the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:24.81,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Do you work, too, Hinako?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:25.67,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:29.28,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine you handling \Nthe work of a waitress, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.51,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,She can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.86,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,But I bet she spills tea all the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:35.52,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,No, she doesn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:36.73,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:37.31,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.83,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if that's what you say, \Nthen let's see you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:42.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:43.92,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.54,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Show her what a great job you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:47.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.60,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:00.90,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,The tea is, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:02.21,sign_8625_100_Milk,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Milk
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.12,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:06.22,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:14.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan, you're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:17.06,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry this was all I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:20.21,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have your outfit cleaned,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:22.61,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,so could you wear this for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:27.31,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... I can't let people \Nsee me dressed like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:28.88,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.44,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You look really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:32.12,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.88,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:45.09,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Aki-chan. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.53,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.26,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:51.76,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I went to see some people \Nfrom my old theater troupe,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:55.51,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,and I lost track of time \Nwhile talking to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.52,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.11,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but you could have sent me \Na message before you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:02.02,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.27,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do that next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:08.28,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chiaki-senpai looks so beautiful today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.80,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:11.16,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,It's so rare to see her in a skirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:13.73,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,She's my idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:16.54,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yua-chan, you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:18.07,Italics Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:21.75,Italics Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan's regular clothes are \Na lot more unique than I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.65,Italics Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,So cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:25.11,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,So beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:28.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:31.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.64,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,what brings you here, Yua-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:38.02,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, I came to lend you some DVDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.64,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Performances by my favorite \Nsmall theater troupes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.65,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,and acting lessons on DVD!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:46.19,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Watch these and study them carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.53,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I can borrow those?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:53.16,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's no big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:56.03,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get better, \NI'll have no competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:59.06,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,And as a fellow actress \Nin the Hitotose Troupe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:03.17,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:05.44,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't get the wrong idea, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.36,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,It's not for you—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:08.55,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You really are nice, Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:11.25,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:14.74,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,They're more like a mother and child \Nthan fellow actresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:12.77,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:15.34,Main Dialogue Top,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I'm not doing this for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:15.83,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.43,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to watch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:25.76,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Today was a lot of fun. I even \Ngot to spend time with Yua-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:29.44,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she came to see me, \Neven though it's summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:33.32,Flashback Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,And as a fellow actress \Nin the Hitotose Troupe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:38.33,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to be part of a group \Nof friends who help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.75,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to go to bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:46.33,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll watch just a little bit \Nof the DVDs Yua-chan lent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:49.59,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:02.85,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll watch this and do my best \Nto aim for the Suzuran stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:09.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:11.04,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even play a DVD?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:13.99,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Just how deep in the \Ncountryside did you live?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.41,sign_13404_165_Coffee_Shop,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Coffee Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:31.17,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, w-welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:33.92,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Help yourself to an open seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:38.34,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll be able to manage today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:41.18,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do my best \Nto help out after this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:42.35,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:43.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:46.06,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Would you go and take the customer's order?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.06,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:53.32,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,H-Have you decided \Nwh-what you'd like to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:55.06,Main Dialogue Top,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:56.19,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:59.27,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,W-Will that be all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:09:59.82,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:05.95,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then please wait a... a... moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:12.84,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:14.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.25,Main Dialogue,Chaiki,0000,0000,0000,,37.5 degrees...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:29.73,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Hina-chan caught a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:32.37,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we should take her to a clinic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:34.60,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should contact her parents, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:37.64,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. It's just a mild fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.86,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just keep an eye on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:44.48,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You can go on and get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:46.50,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:50.13,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay. Sorry I lost my cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:52.29,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that Hina-chan passed out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:54.32,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Should I call an ambulance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:56.40,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I carry her myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:58.30,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You need to calm down, too, Kuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:05.08,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! You're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:08.30,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan... What did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.38,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You came down with a fever and \Npassed out while waiting on a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:13.63,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What? Who's working the coffee shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:16.32,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan is handling it on her own for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:19.46,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going to help her later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.43,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:25.12,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:27.33,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Don't worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:30.76,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, is there anything \Nwe can get for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:35.04,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.34,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,so something warm might be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:41.30,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll warm you \Nwith my own body right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.59,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm warm-blooded!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:45.12,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,How's that, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.90,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you warm now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:49.60,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, v-very warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:54.35,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You know you can't do that. \NWe need to let her rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:58.11,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hina-chan, I'll be back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.03,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:04.54,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take your order?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:06.15,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clean that up right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:09.89,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! You here, Hinako?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.87,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-sama brought more DVDs to lend you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.63,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yua-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:18.50,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hinako caught a cold and passed out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:22.68,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, so I'm looking up things \Nthat help with colds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.22,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,To cure a cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:31.14,Signs,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Dictionary of Medicines
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:27.08,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! She needs medicine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:34.14,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,We can cure Hina-chan with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:38.23,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:40.66,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:48.07,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, I brought something \Nthat'll help your cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:51.83,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da! Say goodbye to your cold with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:53.95,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A green onion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:57.08,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Apparently you \Nwrap it around your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.85,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it in a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:01.46,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,So let's wrap it around your neck right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:07.97,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Something just doesn't seem right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:13.38,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's bound to take at least that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:14.85,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isn't that too many?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:17.52,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The more, the better! Everyone knows that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.29,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she gets hungry and eats some,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.22,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there's plenty to spare!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:24.36,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you do have a point there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:28.48,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What else can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:30.04,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:31.25,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,They say that when you have a cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:33.25,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you should sweat it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:40.25,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:50.64,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Really, you two should know better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:53.64,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You made Hina-chan feel even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:55.27,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:58.29,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I feel alive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:00.40,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.89,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Since you got sweaty,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:13.59,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wipe you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:15.29,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:21.06,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Is it too cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:24.05,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:27.67,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,There, all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:31.05,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:39.49,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we'll be downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:40.50,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,If you need anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.29,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,call us with your cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:43.25,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:12.11,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, you don't have to worry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:17.94,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I found a surefire method used all around \Nthe world to cure sickness instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:19.35,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:22.85,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:26.12,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:29.20,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,A bite from the Great White Snake \Ncures any illness—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:30.92,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:45.94,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Gods, hear my prayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.57,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I was just, um... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:51.33,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make so much noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:52.08,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.20,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Rawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.85,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,A bite from a dragon cures any illness—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:11.30,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Again, only if it's a real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:25.72,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Elohim essaim... Elohim essaim... \NI implore you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:27.17,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,This is just, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:29.22,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What good will it do to summon a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:31.72,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, wrong chant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:39.02,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You two aren't allowed to go \Ninto Hina-chan's room anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:40.16,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:41.73,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:43.38,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:46.48,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but the best thing we can do \Nfor her now is to let her rest quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:49.23,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:50.97,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.61,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Could you help me with something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:04.21,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's so quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:14.83,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is the first time\N I've been sick since I came to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:18.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,How many years has it been \Nsince I caught a cold, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:22.19,Flashback Dialogue,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey, Hina-chan! Good work again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:22.56,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,After I started working as a scarecrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:23.66,Flashback Dialogue,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Thanks for helping out every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:25.64,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I spent all my time in \Nthe field with no breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:25.64,Flashback Dialogue,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Here are your vegetables for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:31.28,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Has it been since first grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:35.09,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mom spent the whole day looking after me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:37.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and she made rice gruel for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:50.14,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Mom is at home right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.92,sign_25651_303_Mom,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:52.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she'll answer the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:57.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I miss you, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:18:01.51,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat your rice gruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:04.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,No, Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:05.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,If I show her any weakness,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:08.51,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she'll tell me to come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:13.77,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I decided I wouldn't go home \Nuntil I started acting in Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:15.94,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and got over my scarecrow problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:21.50,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.53,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Just for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:26.81,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:28.29,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:30.04,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:32.72,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You're not sleeping! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:35.92,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh... This is just, um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.44,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, do you feel hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:38.93,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:41.87,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,We all made some rice gruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.05,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:48.31,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:54.63,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who cut up the \Npickled plum so it'd be easier to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:57.25,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And I cut up the seaweed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:18:59.32,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.33,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Say, "Ahh."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:10.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.96,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:14.82,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:17.92,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes just like my mom's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.47,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:22.74,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:24.58,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:29.76,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because we made it \Nwith the same feelings your mom did?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:31.48,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The same feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:37.23,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,We all made it with the wish \Nthat your cold would get better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.72,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:54.25,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:56.65,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Can you eat more?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:58.46,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll have more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.27,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.27,0:20:02.57,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't \Nget sick to your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:04.68,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll feed you next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:06.80,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "Ahh."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:10.93,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn next!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:17.35,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,S-Say, "Ahh."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:21.69,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:24.57,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It tastes delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:26.48,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll go next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:28.14,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I want another turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.38,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,No fair going twice in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:31.83,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:37.74,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:42.54,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I felt a little homesick today \Nbecause of my cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:46.09,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,but thanks to everyone here, \NI didn't feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:49.25,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting such wonderful new friends
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:52.48,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,makes me glad I moved to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:05.86,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:09.06,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:11.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you guys, I'm all bet— huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.55,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:22.34,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:26.76,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,No! This time, I'm the one \Nwho needs to work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:36.86,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Towel, towel, towel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.03,0:21:40.50,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Fresh clothes, fresh clothes, \Nfresh clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.41,0:21:43.78,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And water... Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:45.78,sign_31260_368_Oral_Medicine__N,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Oral Medicine \NNakajima Yua \NDirections \NTake 3 per day for 7 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:53.36,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Hinako feels better...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:34.22,sign_33687_370_We_ll_Have_a_Tra,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,6000)}We'll Have a Training Camp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:29.57,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan's mom is going to come visit soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.57,0:23:33.55,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And the Hitotose Troupe will finally \Nhold its first performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:37.03,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do to make it successful \Nis practice, practice, practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.03,0:23:39.17,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "We'll Have a Training Camp."
